inent, persistent and actionable"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"communication. Alert message includes functional icon and semantic colour, and may include as well a close button and\/or action link."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Alert Message does not disappear automatically and remains visible until dismissed or resolved by the user."}],"kind":"symbol"}}}